Class AbstractRestRouteProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.rest.AbstractRestRouteProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RestRouteProvider
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuditRestRouteProvider, CoreRestRouteProvider, EntitlementsRestRouteProvider, OAuth2RestRouteProvider, PushNotificationRestRouteProvider, ScriptingRestRouteProvider, SelfServiceRestRouteProvider, SmsRestRouteProvider, UmaRestRouteProvider
    public abstract class AbstractRestRouteProvider
extends Object
implements RestRouteProvider
    An abstract implementation of the RestRouteProvider that provides methods for adding resource (CREST) endpoints and service (CHF REST) endpoints on either the root router or realm router.
    Since:
    13.0.0
